{"tid":1449934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:11:53.000Z","uid":36708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8001687a46d5ce219409b57a25efa88bacea9d57","tid":1449934,"uid":36708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcptTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=bbd97b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcptTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=60e296c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"a4339ace73c2f26daf96b0da3818e3e9c4da52c9","tid":1449934,"uid":82453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f85483de14760d631ebb093e5189f31dbf67a41","tid":1449934,"uid":229106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}